WebWish is released under the zlib license (above), the same license as
Simple DirectMedia Layer (SDL). The core file `driver/SDL_wstiles.c` is
derived from SDL's `SDL_jsmpeg.c` video driver.

Third-party libraries the driver links against (not included in this
repository) carry their own licenses:
  - libwebsockets  — MIT
  - zlib           — zlib license
  - libaom (AV1)   — BSD-2-Clause  (optional, only with WSTILES_HAVE_AV1)
